02 Jun 2019 11:42






The IWW is short for the Industrial Workers of the World, a socialist labor union that considers modern law enforcement to be actively hostile enemies of both their own members and the common people as a whole. It’s damn near impossible to both be a member of the IWW and like the police. Cici Helio, not coincidentally, holds membership in the IWW.

As for the lines about certified cannibals, that’s just something you’re supposed to suspend your disbelief of and consider to be accurate for the sake of fridge horror. If the Foundation has certified cannibals, then there must be some truly unsavory things to use them for — such as testing pork to see if it tastes human. It ultimately boils down to how far you think the Foundation is willing to go to preserve normalcy.





